OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1782888477
OL,3,CTwo arrested after crash left an
OL,4,Cambulance on its side
OL,6,FTwo men have been arrested as police
OL,7,Fcontinue to investigate a crash on the
OL,8,FA23 in West Sussex between a private
OL,9,Fambulance and a Mercedes.
OL,11,FThey were travelling northbound at
OL,12,FPease Pottage when they collided on
OL,13,FSaturday (27 June) around 7.30am.
OL,15,FThe ambulance - which was not carrying
OL,16,Fpatients at the time - crossed
OL,17,Fdirectly in front of a tipper truck
OL,18,Fbefore rolling onto its side.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
