PN,38803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1782888477
OL,3,CTwo arrested after crash left an
OL,4,Cambulance on its side
OL,6,FA 29-year-old man from Rudgewick, was
OL,7,Farrested on suspicion of dangerous
OL,8,Fdriving, failing to stop after a road
OL,9,Ftraffic accident and drug driving.
OL,11,FBoth have been released on bail for
OL,12,Ffurther enquiries.
OL,14,FOfficers are also seeking dashcam and
OL,15,FCCTV footage of the Mercedes being
OL,16,Fdriven from Brighton.
